20 but remain unpaid and a statement that the same has not been
21 redeemed, the total amount of all delinquent taxes, costs, penalties
22 and interest accrued, due and unpaid on the same, and a statement
23 that such real estate will be sold to the highest bidder for cash.
24 It shall not be necessary to set forth the amount of taxes,
